---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Legal & Trust Center — BlocFeed">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-100/40 to-white">
    <br><br><br>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-24 lg:px-8 lg:pt-32 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Legal & Trust Center
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        BlocFeed is built on trust, transparency, and respect. Below you’ll find our Terms of Service, Privacy Policy, and Community Guidelines — the foundation of how we work together to keep this platform safe, fair, and inspiring.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms of Service -->
  <section id="terms" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Terms of Service</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
      These Terms govern your use of BlocFeed. By creating an account or using the platform, you agree to follow them. They are designed to protect both you and the community.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-gray-600">
      <p><strong>Eligibility:</strong> You must be at least 13 years old to use BlocFeed. If you are under 18, you must have parental or guardian consent. By using BlocFeed, you confirm that you meet these requirements.</p>
      <p><strong>Accounts:</strong> You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity under your account. If you suspect unauthorized use, you must notify us immediately.</p>
      <p><strong>Content Ownership:</strong> You retain ownership of the ideas and content you post. By posting, you grant BlocFeed a non‑exclusive license to display, distribute, and promote your content within the platform. We will never claim ownership of your intellectual property.</p>
      <p><strong>Prohibited Use:</strong> You may not use BlocFeed for unlawful activity, harassment, spam, exploitation, or infringement of intellectual property rights. Attempts to manipulate the platform, misrepresent identity, or harm other users are strictly forbidden.</p>
      <p><strong>Termination:</strong> We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms, harm the community, or pose security risks. You may also close your account at any time.</p>
      <p><strong>Changes:</strong> We may update these Terms periodically. Continued use of BlocFeed after changes means you accept the updated Terms.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Policy -->
  <section id="privacy" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
      Your privacy matters. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use BlocFeed.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-gray-600">
      <p><strong>Information We Collect:</strong> We collect information you provide (such as your name, email, and profile details) and data about how you use BlocFeed (such as posts, interactions, and device information).</p>
      <p><strong>How We Use It:</strong> We use your information to provide and improve our services, personalize your experience, communicate with you, and ensure platform security.</p>
      <p><strong>Sharing:</strong> We do not sell your personal data. We may share information with trusted service providers who help us operate BlocFeed, comply with legal obligations, or protect our community.</p>
      <p><strong>Security:</strong> We use industry‑standard measures to protect your data, including encryption and access controls. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.</p>
      <p><strong>Your Rights:</strong> You can update or delete your account information at any time. You may also request access to the data we hold about you. For more details, contact <a href="mailto:legal@bloccfeed.space" class="text-indigo-600 underline">legal@bloccfeed.space</a>.</p>
      <p><strong>Retention:</strong> We retain your information only as long as necessary to provide services or comply with legal obligations.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Guidelines -->
  <section id="guidelines" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Community Guidelines</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
      BlocFeed is a space for creativity, collaboration, and respect. To keep it safe and inspiring, we ask all members to follow these guidelines.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-gray-600">
      <p><strong>Respect Others:</strong> Treat fellow creators with kindness. Harassment, hate speech, discrimination, or personal attacks are not tolerated.</p>
      <p><strong>Originality:</strong> Share your own ideas or give proper credit when building on others’ work. Plagiarism or misrepresentation of ownership is prohibited.</p>
      <p><strong>Safety:</strong> Do not post harmful, illegal, or dangerous content. This includes threats, exploitation, or promotion of violence.</p>
      <p><strong>Constructive Feedback:</strong> Encourage and support others with thoughtful, respectful comments. Criticism should be aimed at helping creators improve, not tearing them down.</p>
      <p><strong>Integrity:</strong> Be honest in your interactions. Do not impersonate others, spread misinformation, or attempt to manipulate the platform.</p>
      <p><strong>Enforcement:</strong> Violations may result in warnings, content removal, or account suspension. Repeated or severe violations may lead to permanent bans.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing CTA -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff80b5]/10 to-[#9089fc]/10 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Questions about our policies?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
        We’re here to help. If you have any concerns about our Terms, Privacy, or Guidelines, reach out to our support team or use the form below to report issues.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Report Abuse Form -->
  <section id="report" class="relative py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center">Report Abuse or Policy Violations</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-center">
        Help us keep BlocFeed safe. If you encounter abuse, harassment, or content that violates our policies, please let us know using the form below.
      </p>

      <form name="report-abuse" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="mt-10 space-y-6 bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="report-abuse" />

        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Your Name</label>
          <input type="text" name="name" id="name" required
                 class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:text-sm"/>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Your Email</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" id="email" required
                 class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:text-sm"/>
        </div>

               <div>
          <label for="details" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Details of Abuse / Violation</label>
          <textarea name="details" id="details" rows="6" required
                    class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:text-sm"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="url" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Link to Content (optional)</label>
          <input type="url" name="url" id="url"
                 placeholder="Paste the URL of the offending content"
                 class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:text-sm"/>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="screenshot" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Additional Information (optional)</label>
          <textarea name="screenshot" id="screenshot" rows="3"
                    placeholder="Provide any extra context or evidence"
                    class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:text-sm"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
          <button type="submit"
                  class="w-full rounded-md bg-black px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-white hover:text-black border border-black">
            Submit Report
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
